I purchased an HP All in One mod 200-5150la in July 2010 and it has been having hard drive (1TB) failures to the point of 2 replacements in a period of 6 months due to "who knows". Now I will be able to keep an eye on the new third one. Program works as described. No problems at all. Thanks a lot
